\begin{equation*}R_{1}=\frac{1}{n_{c}}{{\sum^{n_{c}}_{i=1}}}f \left \left( \left \frac{{v_{i}+ \left \left(-{\mathrm{{\mu}}}_{i}^{<1>}+{\mathrm{{\mu}}}_{i}^{<2>}\right) \right }/{2}}{{ \left \left({\mathrm{{\mu}}}_{i}^{<1>}-{\mathrm{{\mu}}}_{i}^{<2>}\right) \right }/{2}}\right) \right  \right \end{equation*}\end{document} where f(x) = max (−1, min (1, x)), n
c is the number of genes in the classifier, and i = 1, 2, …,n
c is the label for each individual gene in the classifier, μi is the expression level of gene i for the new cell, μi
